\c 3
\s Mukadzi wechipiri weufeve waHosiya
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakati kwandiri: Endazve, ude mukadzi anodikanwa neshamwari \add yake\add*, asi ari chifeve, saJehovha achida vana vaIsraeri, asi vachitarisa kune vamwe vamwari, uye vachida zvingwa zvezvibereko zvemuzambiringa zvakaomeswa.
\v 2 Zvino ndakazvitengera iye nemakobiri esirivha gumi nemashanu, nehomeri* yebhari*, nehafu yehomeri yebhari.
\v 3 Zvino ndakati kwaari: Uchagara uri wangu kwemazuva mazhinji; usaita ufeve uye usava we\add umwe\add* murume, saizvozvo iniwo kwauri.
\v 4 Nokuti vana vaIsraeri vachagara mazuva mazhinji, vasina mambo, uye vasina muchinda, uye vasina chibairo, uye vasina shongwe yechifananidzo, uye vasina efodhi* kana terafimi*.
\v 5 Pashure vana vaIsraeri vachadzoka, zvino vachitsvaka Jehovha Mwari wavo, naDhavhidhi mambo wavo; uye vachauya kuna Jehovha vachitya, nekurunako rwake, pamazuva ekupedzisira.